Biogen's long and winding road in Alzheimer's hits wall  $BIIB $LLY $JNJ 

https://newsfilter.io/a/416df7cbd4f08a3e5e13fcde4162e3dc

links.title: Biogen's long and winding road in Alzheimer's hits wall
links.description: Yesterday's negative FDA advisory committee vote may be the final nail in the coffin in the up-and-down registration path of Biogen and collaboration partner Eisai's aducanumab for the treatment of patients with mild Alzheimer's disease. This is the latest setback for therapies targeting the underlying pathology of AD in which the highest dose achieved the primary endpoint, was insufficient to demonstrate efficacy.
